Class ScenarioPartMetadataVO

java.lang.Object
  edu.cmu.sei.arche.vo.ScenarioPartMetadataVO
public class ScenarioPartMetadataVO
extends java.lang.Object

Describes a scenario part, i.e., gives meta information that is associated with a scenario. This is not a fact in the fact base. It comes from the RF configuration file. *

Author:
Alexander Berendeyev
